<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode.ResetConstantStateValue" Title="ResetConstantStateValue method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode">IProgramNode</PageRef> ->
    ResetConstantStateValue
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ResetConstantStateValue</TypeRef> method removes any constant value which has been previously set by
      the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode.SetConstantStateValue">SetConstantStateValue</PageRef> method for the target shader
      state variable.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void ResetConstantStateValue(StateValueId stateId, size_t arrayIndex = 0);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="StateValueId" Name="value">
          The <TypeRef>StateValueId</TypeRef> of the target state variable
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="size_t" Name="arrayIndex">
          Specifies the index to use if the target state value is an array
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
